external_knowledge:
- "beacons of struggle" symbolically refers to the states with the most active cases;
- "holding the torch of highest active cases" metaphorically indicates the states with the highest number of active cases;
- "most recent quarter" refers to the quarter with the highest year and quarter number.

sql:
SELECT users.user_name, states.state_name
FROM users, states
ORDER BY users.user_name ASC;
